\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces VPER framework architecture. The system flows from User Input through Workspace Cold Start into the Planner $\to $ ReAct-Agent $\to $ Replanner loop. After the loop completes, the Validator evaluates the candidate answer. If accepted, the answer is submitted; if rejected, the Replanner adjusts the plan for another iteration.}}{4}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
